OL,3,CTrans woman Lauren on the struggle to
OL,4,Clive as herself in Northern Ireland
OL,6,FOne of the themes that keeps cutting
OL,7,Fthrough in the UTV podcast Going the
OL,8,FExtra Mile is the idea of creating
OL,9,Fcommunities and supporting each other.
OL,10,FMy guest this week is someone who
OL,11,Fpersonifies these ideals.
OL,13,FLauren is a trans woman who puts
OL,14,Fherself forward to be a local voice
OL,15,Ffor the queer community. Her work has
OL,16,Fmeant that she's recently been
OL,17,Fnominated for British LGBT Awards `
OL,18,Fand last year she won the
OL,19,FInspirational Role Model Award at the
OL,20,Finaugural Northern Ireland Hummingbird
OL,21,FAwards.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
