OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1778861473
OL,3,CTrans woman Lauren on the struggle to
OL,4,Clive as herself in Northern Ireland
OL,6,FShe's a volunteer for Belfast Pride
OL,7,Fand has been crowned the Trans
OL,8,FCommunity Champion for NI at the Trans
OL,9,Fin the City Awards 2025.
OL,11,FThe trans issue can be divisive. For
OL,12,Fas many as there are who support and
OL,13,Fchampion the trans community, there
OL,14,Fare many who do not. So for Lauren, to
OL,15,Fspeak out and be open is as courageous
OL,16,Fas it is vital.
OL,18,FShe is honest and pragmatic.
OL,20,F'You only get one life,' Lauren says.
OL,21,F'I'm not hurting anyone by how I live.'
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
