OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1778861473
OL,3,CTrans woman Lauren on the struggle to
OL,4,Clive as herself in Northern Ireland
OL,6,FIt's a simple phrase but impactful.
OL,7,FWhy do people oppose the decisions of
OL,8,Fpeople who don't have anything to do
OL,9,Fwith them? And yes, we have one life.
OL,10,FDon't we have the right to live it as
OL,11,Fwe like as long as we're not affecting
OL,12,Fanyone else negatively?
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
