OL,3,CTrans woman Lauren on the struggle to
OL,4,Clive as herself in Northern Ireland
OL,6,FLauren admits her own journey has been
OL,7,Fcomplicated, beset with mental health
OL,8,Fissues. But since becoming herself she
OL,9,Fhas found a new confidence that allows
OL,10,Fher to shine in the spotlight. Be it
OL,11,Fwith her cabaret participation or
OL,12,Frunning 'safe-space' activities for
OL,13,Fother members of the trans community,
OL,14,Fshe's thoughtfully creating a
OL,15,Fmeaningful change for others who are
OL,16,Fon the same journey.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
