OL,3,CTrans woman Lauren on the struggle to
OL,4,Clive as herself in Northern Ireland
OL,6,FAnd this is what Going the Extra Mile
OL,7,Fis all about. Giving a platform for
OL,8,Fpeople who give their time, their
OL,9,Fefforts, their attentions for the good
OL,10,Fof others. Enjoy...
OL,12,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,13,FITVX
OL,15,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,16,Fhere.
